wiki.content: "Anything Could Happen" is the first single from Ellie Goulding's second album, Halcyon. It was debuted on 21 August 2012. The video features fan-submitted Instagram photos of the lyrics. 25 year old English singer-songwriter Elena Jane Goulding released her second album “Halcyon” in Oct 2012. The lead single “Anything Could Happen” reached the top 5 in the UK in the same month. Ellie was featured performing the song in the TV ad for a well known headphone brand in Sept 2012.
